meters":{"operation":"append","documentId":{"__rl":true,"mode":"list","value":"","cachedResultName":"Email Tracker"},"sheetName":{"__rl":true,"mode":"name","value":"Main","cachedResultName":"Main"},"columns":{"mappingMode":"autoMapInputData","value":{},"matchingColumns":[],"schema":[]},"options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.googleSheets","typeVersion":4.7,"position":[6453,1420],"id":"37db3802-37a1-4cdd-acf5-62d3c78a2702","name":"Park in Dead-Letter Queue","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000},{"parameters":{"content":"### Receive Inbound Webhook\n\nEntry point: listens for POST calls on `/wf02382-email`. Use the TEST url while building, switch callers to the PRODUCTION url after publishing.\n\nNext: Stamp & Shape Email","width":280,"height":232,"color":5},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-330,520],"id":"357bc79e-3933-1fda-0143-677c1490ef15","name":"Note: Receive Inbound Webhook"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Stamp & Shape Email\n\nShapes the item: writes `messageId`, `receivedAt`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Payload Valid?","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-6,520],"id":"1754d928-e13e-ec03-0819-e53731d6b122","name":"Note: Stamp & Shape Email"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Payload Valid?\n\nTwo-way gate on `={{ $json.messageId }}`. TRUE continues the happy path, FALSE takes the alternate branch.\n\nPorts: ①→ Classify with AI · ②→ Record Rejected Input","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[318,520],"id":"6fd0ee03-50b5-d1b6-ef65-85c9829be389","name":"Note: Payload Valid?"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Record Rejected Input\n\ngoogleSheets — `append` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[318,1030],"id":"3b7c2802-f1d1-12e8-2329-a0216b47f775","name":"Note: Record Rejected Input"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Classify with AI\n\nLLM classification into: Action Needed, Reference, Ignore (+fallback). Output port order matches this list.\n\nPorts: ①→ Store as Action Needed · ②→ Store as Reference, Capture Failure Context · ③→ Store as Ignore · ④→ Alert Slack — Other\n\n⚠ failures exit via the error rail","width":280,"height":232,"color":6},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[642,520],"id":"7b43c9e8-a715-26ee-2b5c-2180fdd2a0d1","name":"Note: Classify with AI"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Anthropic Chat Model\n\nChat model powering the AI step (model: `claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929`). Swap providers here without rewiring.\n\nFeeds **Classify with AI** as `languageModel`\n\n🔑 Anthropic API key","width":280,"height":232,"color":6},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[885,1090],"id":"ab961608-7ee2-1cf8-b02f-a8e9f66f3d63","name":"Note: Anthropic Chat Model"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Store as Action Needed\n\ngoogleSheets — `append` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Reunite Branches · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1209,40],"id":"274057bc-4c1b-52cf-3a64-bf3a6ebb831f","name":"Note: Store as Action Needed"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Store as Reference\n\ngoogleSheets — `append` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Reunite Branches · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1533,490],"id":"11c23dc5-9f5b-7019-cf46-325938074917","name":"Note: Store as Reference"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Store as Ignore\n\ngoogleSheets — `append` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Reunite Branches · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1857,940],"id":"b243dd95-d670-6827-e80d-e6a66649bfe7","name":"Note: Store as Ignore"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Alert Slack — Other\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Reunite Branches · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2181,1390],"id":"595e40d7-c24e-0100-c224-d44d61b59750","name":"Note: Alert Slack — Other"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Reunite Branches\n\nRejoins 4 branches into one stream (mode: append) so downstream logic runs once.\n\nNext: Fingerprint for Idempotency","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2829,520],"id":"94cf4719-39fd-848d-2e6b-29e58800eb14","name":"Note: Reunite Branches"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Fingerprint for Idempotency\n\nCustom JavaScript: Build a stable idempotency key per email (djb2 hash, no deps)\n\nNext: Drop Already-Processed Items","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3801,520],"id":"017966eb-8f32-cc6c-0254-72cc15bd6b4c","name":"Note: Fingerprint for Idempotency"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Drop Already-Processed Items\n\nCross-execution dedupe: remembers keys it has processed before and drops repeats — the idempotency guard.\n\nNext: Serialize Run Output (CSV)","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4125,520],"id":"70cfea6b-b77a-600c-6de1-4523918893b6","name":"Note: Drop Already-Processed Items"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Serialize Run Output (CSV)\n\nSerializes items to a CSV binary file.\n\nNext: Archive Row Snapshot","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4449,520],"id":"225c37c4-1fa9-cd5b-1c31-47de2cce74e1","name":"Note: Serialize Run Output (CSV)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Archive Row Snapshot\n\ngoogleSheets — `append` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Enrich with Reference Data · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4773,520],"id":"51df42d8-62f2-f9bf-1749-7f0590010e8f","name":"Note: Archive Row Snapshot"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Enrich with Reference Data\n\nGET https://enrichment.example.com/v2/lookup — retries 3× with backoff on failure.\n\nPorts: ①→ Fold In Enrichment Fields · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 API key / bearer for the target API","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5097,520],"id":"32a8fcf0-cc69-2e43-1835-d1dd1915a7ff","name":"Note: Enrich with Reference Data"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Fold In Enrichment Fields\n\nShapes the item: writes `enrichedAt`, `enrichmentSource`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Summarize Run Stats","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5421,520],"id":"887b1da7-c97d-57ff-7fb4-affe3d3abffb","name":"Note: Fold In Enrichment Fields"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Summarize Run Stats\n\nShapes the item: writes `runAt`, `itemCount`, `status`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5745,520],"id":"7eaafe3b-351c-7239-b688-243b448473c7","name":"Note: Summarize Run Stats"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)\n\ngoogleSheets — `append` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Send Summary to Slack · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[6069,520],"id":"9a3b1e90-8512-e317-7550-62d4bce7406e","name":"Note: Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Send Summary to Slack\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[6393,520],"id":"12fff2de-b002-0540-81e5-f281899ec8fb","name":"Note: Send Summary to Slack"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Capture Failure Context\n\nShapes the item: writes `failedNode`, `errorMessage`, `workflow`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Escalate Failure to Twilio","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5745,1540],"id":"a9968168-77be-df1e-7fa2-98ca68955716","name":"Note: Capture Failure Context"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Escalate Failure to Twilio\n\ntwilio — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\nNext: Park in Dead-Letter Queue\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Twilio SID + token","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[6069,1540],"id":"2d4a8b2f-2115-0743-d2b3-c063cdfd7911","name":"Note: Escalate Failure to Twilio"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Park in Dead-Letter Queue\n\ngoogleSheets — `append` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[6393,1540],"id":"0da7360b-a433-c92e-fe19-0558c2c81fa0","name":"Note: Park in Dead-Letter Queue"},{"parameters":{"content":"# Summarize long emails with Google Sheets and Twilio hands-free\n\n**Pattern:** AI Summarize & Route · **Level:** Production · **Trigger:** Webhook\n\n## What it does\nSummarize long emails with Google Sheets and Twilio hands-free. It fires the moment an external system calls its webhook.\n\n## Why it exists\nManual newsletters is slow and error-prone; this workflow makes the process repeatable, monitored and hands-off, with failures surfaced instead of silently lost.\n\n## Main flow\nReceive Inbound Webhook → Stamp & Shape Email → Payload Valid? → Classify with AI → Store as Action Needed → Reunite Branches → Fingerprint for Idempotency → …\n\n## Use it for\n- Teams that want to ai summarize & route without manual effort\n- Anyone automating newsletters in marketing\n- Replacing a fragile manual process with a reliable workflow\n\n## You get\n- Responds in seconds\n- Keeps your systems in sync\n- Saves hours of manual work each week\n\n## Before first run\nConnect credentials: API key / bearer for the target API; Anthropic API key; Google OAuth2 / service account; Slack OAuth2; Twilio SID + token.\nFollow the color key: 🟦 entry · 🟪 AI · 🟫 actions · ⬜ utilities · 🟩 outputs · 🟥 error rail.\nEach node has its own doc card underneath — read those before editing.","width":480,"height":900},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-830,80],"id":"70eb0383-6034-3e4c-dff0-0debbe0b79aa","name":"📘 Workflow Overview"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛟 Error handling & retries\n\nExternal calls retry **3× with 2s backoff**. Anything still failing exits through its node's error output into the red error rail → context is captured and the on-call channel is alerted. Failures are also parked in a dead-letter queue for replay. Set an n8n **Error Workflow** in settings as the final safety net.","width":360,"height":260,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-230,-500],"id":"c43e0d95-f698-f9c0-7d09-e9936d44f8d0","name":"🛟 Error handling & retries"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🔐 Security\n\nNever trust inbound payloads: the webhook path is unguessable. Add header auth or IP allow-listing for defense in depth. Secrets live in n8n credentials — never in node parameters.","width":360,"height":260,"color":1},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[190,-500],"id":"64f4327d-9bea-7f48-7f70-553b8876fdc9","name":"🔐 Security"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🤖 AI cluster\n\nPurple nodes form one AI unit: the root node orchestrates, sub-nodes plug in via typed ports (model / memory / tools / parser). Swap the chat model without rewiring anything else. Costs scale with tokens — keep prompts lean and cap iterations.","width":360,"height":260,"color":6},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[610,-500],"id":"8d5963a6-ec69-28d9-b02a-049ca19cd65d","name":"🤖 AI cluster"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛠 Customize me\n\nQuick wins: point the data nodes at your own accounts (see 🔑 lines on each card), adjust the trigger cadence, and tune thresholds/labels to your newsletters process. Every node card explains its role — safe to extend at any marked branch.","width":360,"height":260,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1030,-500],"id":"bf0a6a32-8147-da95-e840-a81ff8c28e64","name":"🛠 Customize me"}],"connections":{"Receive Inbound Webhook":{"main":[[{"node":"Stamp & Shape Email","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Stamp & Shape Email":{"main":[[{"node":"Payload Valid?","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Payload Valid?":{"main":[[{"node":"Classify with AI","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Record Rejected Input","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Anthropic Chat Model":{"ai_languageModel":[[{"node":"Classify with AI","type":"ai_languageModel","index":0}]]},"Classify with AI":{"main":[[{"node":"Store as Action Needed","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Store as Reference","type":"main","index":0},{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Store as Ignore","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Alert Slack — Other","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Store as Action Needed":{"main":[[{"node":"Reunite Branches","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Store as Reference":{"main":[[{"node":"Reunite Branches","type":"main","index":1}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Store as Ignore":{"main":[[{"node":"Reunite Branches","type":"main","index":2}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Alert Slack — Other":{"main":[[{"node":"Reunite Branches","type":"main","index":3}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Reunite Branches":{"main":[[{"node":"Fingerprint for Idempotency","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Fingerprint for Idempotency":{"main":[[{"node":"Drop Already-Processed Items","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Drop Already-Processed Items":{"main":[[{"node":"Serialize Run Output (CSV)","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Serialize Run Output (CSV)":{"main":[[{"node":"Archive Row Snapshot","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Archive Row Snapshot":{"main":[[{"node":"Enrich with Reference Data","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Enrich with Reference Data":{"main":[[{"node":"Fold In Enrichment Fields","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Fold In Enrichment Fields":{"main":[[{"node":"Summarize Run Stats","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Summarize Run Stats":{"main":[[{"node":"Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)":{"main":[[{"node":"Send Summary to Slack","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Capture Failure Context":{"main":[[{"node":"Escalate Failure to Twilio","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Escalate Failure to Twilio":{"main":[[{"node":"Park in Dead-Letter Queue","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Send Summary to Slack":{"main":[[],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]}},"active":false,"settings":{"executionOrder":"v1"},"meta":{"templateCredsSetupCompleted":false},"tags":[],"pinData":{},"versionId":"d935a529-c176-41b7-bc3b-94ac3d543ba4","id":"FDX02382"}